---
description: Converting Storybook .mdx to 11ty .md files
globs: *.md
---
1. Frontmatter Rules:

- Always include the basic frontmatter with title, layout, and tag
- Add associatedElements array when the component has related elements that are referenced in API tags


2. Story Parameters Format:

- Use quotes around height values and include "px" unit
- Follow pattern: '{ "inline": false, "height": "600px" }'
- Not: { "inline": false, height: 600 }


3. Component Conversion:

- Convert <Canvas of={Story}> to {% story 'component', 'Story' %}
- Convert <nve-api-detail> to {% api 'component', 'type', 'value' %}

- Remove <nve-api-summary>, <nve-api-status> and <nve-api-table> sections
- Preserve all descriptive text and HTML examples
Keep section structure and hierarchy intact


4. File Organization:

- Maintain installation section with code examples
- Group related sections together (e.g., all layout variations)
- Keep ARIA spec links and other external references
- Add trailing newline at end of file